Class Interface<Interest>

java.lang.Object
User.Interface<Interest>
Type Parameters:
Interest -
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Interface<Interest> extends Object implements Serializable
This interface serves both customers and couriers: For customers: It displays special offers for those who have opted in to receive them. For couriers: It lists available orders for potential completion.
